msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:40
msgid "Leads can be generated for :guilabel:`Companies` to get company information only, or for |CC| to get both company information and contact information for individual employees."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:43
msgid "Filtering options for generating leads include the following:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:45
msgid ":guilabel:`Countries`: Filter leads based on the country (or countries) they are located in."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:46
msgid ":guilabel:`States`: Filter leads even further based on the state in which they are located, if applicable."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:48
msgid ":guilabel:`Industries`: Filter leads based on the specific industry they work in."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:49
msgid ":guilabel:`Filter on Size`: Generates a field labeled :guilabel:`Size`. Fill in the blanks to create a range for the desired company size based on its number of employees."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:53
msgid "When using |CC|, generated contacts can also be filtered based on their :guilabel:`Role` or :guilabel:`Seniority`."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:56
msgid "Additionally, there are options for sales team assignment and internal tracking:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:58
msgid ":guilabel:`Sales Team`: Set which Sales Team the leads will be assigned to."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:59
msgid ":guilabel:`Salesperson`: Set which member of the Sales Team the leads will be assigned to."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:60
msgid ":guilabel:`Default Tags`: Set which tags are applied directly to the leads once found."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/acquire_leads/lead_mining.rst:63
