#: ../../content/applications/sales/crm/performance/win_loss.rst:90
msgid "The **CRM** app uses the features of the **Marketing Automation** app for tracking campaign-related statistics. For more information about campaigns, mediums, and sources, :doc:`see the Marketing Automation documentation <../../../marketing/marketing_automation>`."
