#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:8
msgid "Milestone-based invoicing is designed for companies that deliver work in clearly defined phases. Instead of invoicing an entire service upfront or at the very end, businesses can bill customers progressively as each stage of work is completed. This approach provides customers clearer visibility into progress and value delivered over time."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/sales/invoicing/milestone.rst:13
msgid "In Odoo, milestone invoicing is configured at the product level in the **Sales** app, with milestone progress and completion managed in the **Projects** app. When a milestone is marked as reached, the delivered quantity on the sales order (SO) is updated and can be invoiced."
