msgid "Once these steps are complete, payment providers will be able to create tokens with customers' saved payment details during the checkout process. Saved payment details can then be used for future online or recurring subscription charges. Customers can also log into their :doc:`customer portal <../../general/users/user_portals>` and enter their payment information there."
