#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:60
msgid "Being marked :guilabel:`Contract in exception` prevents scheduled actions from running, which keeps the system from accidentally double-charging the customer if the automatic payment actually went through. Because the status of the payment failed to register with the system, users must manually check if the payment has been made before automatic payments and other scheduled actions can resume."
msgstr ""

#: ../../content/applications/sales/subscriptions/automatic_payments.rst:65
